# 🎉 Event Guest List Manager

A dynamic and interactive guest list manager built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Users can add guests, categorize them, toggle RSVP status, edit or remove names, and enjoy a sleek green-themed interface with a full-page party background.

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ Add guest names via a form
- ✅ Categorize guests as *Friend*, *Family*, or *Colleague*
- ✅ Automatically timestamp when guests are added
- ✅ Toggle RSVP status (Attending/Not Attending)
- ✅ Edit or remove guests dynamically
- ✅ Guest limit set to 10, with alert when exceeded
- ✅ Stylish green buttons for RSVP, Edit, and Remove
- ✅ Responsive layout with Tailwind-style CSS
- ✅ Background party image for immersive experience

---

## 🚀 How to Run

1. **Clone the Repository**  
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/event-guest-list-manager.git
   cd event-guest-list-manager
Open in Browser
Simply open index.html in your preferred web browser.

